<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Help Page</title>
    <link
      rel="icon"
      type="image/x-icon"
      href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/53/Pok%C3%A9_Ball_icon.svg"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="flex justify-center items-center min-h-screen bg-gray-800">
    <div
      class="bg-gray-600 border-8 border-red-600 shadow-xl w-full h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-6"
    >
      <!-- Naviiiiii -->

      <nav class="absolute top-6 left-4">
        <a
          href="/dash"
          class="bg-red-600 text-white font-mono text-lg px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border-2 border-red-800 shadow-lg hover:bg-red-500 hover:border-red-700"
        >
          Return to Dashboard
        </a>
      </nav>

      <!-- Replace Text with Image -->
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
        <img
          src="/images/Help-1-28-2025.png"
          alt="Help"
          class="w-[300px] md:w-[400px]"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Help Section Container -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-full">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 w-full max-w-5xl mt-8">
          <!-- Pokédex Help -->
          <div
            class="bg-red-500 text-black font-bold p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-black h-64 w-full flex flex-col justify-center"
          >
            <h2 class="text-xl text-center">Pokédex Help</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-center font-normal mt-2">
              The Pokédex feature is here to help you search through Pokémon and
              be able to see more about them. You can use filters to search
              specific types or generations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Team Building -->
          <div
            class="bg-purple-400 text-black font-bold p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-black h-64 w-full flex flex-col justify-center"
          >
            <h2 class="text-xl text-center">Team Building</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-center font-normal mt-2">
              Team building can take lots of time and work. The best way to work
              on building a team is to think of a concept and search through
              Pokémon that can help fulfill that goal.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Badges -->
          <div
            class="bg-blue-500 text-black font-bold p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-black h-64 w-full flex flex-col justify-center"
          >
            <h2 class="text-xl text-center">Badges</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-center font-normal mt-2">
              Badges are unlocked through making different kinds of teams. Each
              badge has different requirements. Some will be based off types,
              weaknesses, or super effectiveness.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
